    dc:description "FIG. 1. — Micronella najtae n. sp.: A, dorsal chaetotaxy; B, ventral chaetotaxy; C, PAO and its surrounding chaetae. Abbreviations: see Material and methods. Scale bars: A, B, 0.1 mm; C, 0.03 mm." ;
